---
import MiFoto from "../../assets/img/16.jpg";
---

<!-- Contenedor principal -->
<div
  class="mx-auto mt-20 flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-center gap-8 px-6 lg:flex-row "
>
  <!-- Imagen -->
  <div
    class="border-primary h-64 w-64 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg md:h-96 md:w-96 drop-shadow-[4px_4px_0_#7836cf]"
  >
    <img
      src={MiFoto.src}
      alt="Farnaz Boroumand"
      class="h-full w-full object-cover"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Texto -->
  <div class="flex-1 text-center text-gray-300 lg:text-left">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">
      My name is <span class="text-white text-shadow">Farnaz</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4">
      I'm from <span class="text-primary font-semibold">Tehran, Iran</span> and I am currently
      a <span class="text-primary font-semibold"
        >Software Engineering Student</span
      > and <span class="text-primary font-semibold"
        >Programmer</span
      >, specializing in <span class="text-primary font-semibold"
        >Backend Development</span
      >, <span class="text-primary font-semibold">IoT Systems</span>, and
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">Telegram Bot Development</span>,
      using technologies like <span class="text-primary italic"
        >PHP, Python, Flutter, Dart, JavaScript, and various IoT frameworks</span
      >.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2">
      I am currently pursuing my <span class="text-primary font-semibold"
        >Bachelor's degree in Software Engineering</span
      > at <span class="text-primary font-semibold">Dr. Shariati Technical and Vocational University</span>. My passion for <span
        class="text-primary font-semibold">technology</span
      > and <span class="text-primary font-semibold">programming</span> has led me to work on diverse projects including
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">CRM development</span>, <span class="text-primary font-semibold">smart home systems</span>, and
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">mobile applications</span>. I have experience in both
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">freelance work</span> and
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">corporate environments</span>, always seeking to expand my knowledge and skills.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2">
      I am committed to <span class="text-primary font-semibold"
        >continuous learning</span
      > and
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">growth</span> in my abilities,
      adapting to new
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">technological advances</span> and challenging myself
      at both
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">professional</span> and <span
        class="text-primary font-semibold">personal</span
      > levels.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
